room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Escape Hour Gig Harbor in Gig Harbor
review: We did the Cabin room. It was so much fun very tricky to figure out. We didn't beat the clock but we will be back to win next time!! Definitely recommend going here!

room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Escape Hour Gig Harbor in Gig Harbor
review: We had so much fun today! We barely missed escaping The Cabin. Definitely a great date night though and the staff was fabulous as well! We laughed quite a bit. Thanks for everything!

room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Escape Hour Gig Harbor in Gig Harbor
review: Everything about our Cabin experience today was top notch! Kelsy was an amazing host. All the staff were very personable and funny except Drew who I think scared us a few times (stood the hairs up on our skin). Can't wait to check out other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Escape Hour Gig Harbor in Gig Harbor
review: Took my son for his 14th bday, his friends and my 19-year-old daughter. We did THE CABIN and I️t was pretty awesone. Usually don’t do scary but I️ did this and I’m still here haha

room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Escape Hour Gig Harbor in Gig Harbor
review: Very good room with good props and puzzles. This is our groups 8th room and we did not escape the cabin. Nice people, nice facility.
